%% Parent-order execution — signal to venue fills
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as Strategy
    participant P as PreTradeValidator
    participant K as RiskManager
    participant R as ExecutionRouter
    participant W as AlgoWheel
    participant SL as Slicer
    participant V as VwapExecutor
    participant O as OrderManager
    participant G as Gateway
    participant T as ExecutionTracker

    S->>P: Signal (optional group_id for pairs)
    alt pair group
        P->>P: validate_group · unified qty floor
    else single leg
        P->>P: validate_single
    end
    P->>K: capped qty · exposure · spread veto
    K-->>P: approved / rejected
    P->>R: ParentOrder request
    R->>W: features → FRONTLOAD | NORMAL | BACKLOAD
    W-->>R: AlgoMode
    R->>SL: slice weights (qty conserved)
    R->>T: record arrival mid
    loop each slice until filled or timeout
        R->>V: schedule slice
        V->>O: ChildOrder LIMIT (peg bid/ask)
        O->>G: place_order(clientOrderId deterministic)
        G-->>O: ack
        G-->>O: fills (partial OK)
        alt slice timeout or slippage breach
            V->>O: cancel child
            V->>G: market residual (reduce_only if exit)
        end
    end
    O-->>T: fill stream
    T-->>R: PARENT_UPDATE on each fill
    T-->>R: EXECUTION_REPORT on parent done
